body_html:
I have enabled MKL-DNN in the builds of the JavaCPP Presets for TensorFlow:
https://github.com/bytedeco/javacpp-presets/tree/master/tensorflow
With those builds, it's possible to use both the official Java API and the C/C++ API from Java...
